Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:20.77,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.07,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:29.89,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:43.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:49.52,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between\Nthe sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.75,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good\Ntime just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:07.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.34,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.28,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:26.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:30.23,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.78,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:41.99,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing,\Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:49.04,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave\Nthe rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.53,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.74,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.74,0:02:00.08,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:02.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.87,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.87,0:02:06.62,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:08.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:09.85,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.47,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.98,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.64,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:15.71,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.91,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.65,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.00,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.19,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:35.54,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:39.51,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:42.67,Italics,song,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, \Na boy whose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become\N the next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.60,0:03:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and\N less able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking a ship coating craftsman \Nto help them reach Fishman Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hat crew landed \Non the Sabaody Archipelago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where they met Rayleigh, a craftsman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the former vice-captain \Nof the Roger Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and company had decided to \Nhide while Rayleigh coats the Sunny,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when Bartholomew Kuma, \None of the Seven Warlords of the Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,appeared before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Diable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mouton...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Jet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...600 Pound...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Zoro had doubts about this Kuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a fake, then \Nthat's the real problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd mean there are two \Nguys who're this strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the rookies \Ntook on Admiral Kizaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an assassin sent by Navy Headquarters, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Borsalino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, Uncle! You do \Nhave a Baby Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you contact me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sentomaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me, "Oh!" What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the island now, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wasn't able to get \Na hold of you, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! Just get to work now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits have split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy, \NCaptain Kid, Trafalgar Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do we start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't say? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ain't Bartholomew Kuma, \Nthen who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look exactly like\N the Warlord of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's goin' on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"An Even Stronger Enemy Appears! \NThe Battle Axe-Carrying Sentomaru"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:27.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell outta here, Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.82,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking this guy down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:36.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's in the way, Eustass-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Warlord of the Sea, \Nyet all you can do is shoot beams?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Trafalgar Law, \Ncaptain of the Heart Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Eustass Captain Kid, \Ncaptain of the Kid Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Now there's a whole load of marines!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for us to get stuck here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're bustin' straight through! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Jean Bart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the new guy! Don't give me orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard took all the fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Bartholomew Kuma, \None of the Seven Warlords of the Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! There's not even time to strike back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro!\N--That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoofprint...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Blizzard Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Boxing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spider Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hand-to-hand combat \Nabilities are insane, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Get ready, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swallow Bon en Avant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm already dead, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is no time to be saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Atlas Comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That was scary! Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh? He's acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Now explosives work on him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One went in his mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something shorted out inside his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body's hard, but he still bleeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like me, a regular living person
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whose body has been modified with weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Look out! He's spotted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochenta Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuatro Mano
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The beam went off inside his mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He blew himself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt your little break, mister,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's a lightning advisory \Nright where you're standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the dark clouds to the Climate Baton!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Lance Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That had quite an effect! Spectacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't affect him at all! \NHe's still in tip-top shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is he aiming at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he acting out of desperation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The freak's starting to go berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give in to despair and the fight's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Knock him this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you to be stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flambé Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! He's finally starting to fall apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.49,0:13:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Aura Kyutôryu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro multiplied!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nine Lightening Slashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gear Third!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one last push!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush him, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shrinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stopped the bastard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it had to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's creepy... \NIt looks like it could still start moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does, we're done for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worn out I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should've run away \Ninstead of fighting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's best to defeat \Nwhoever we can ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are being chased, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, after all is said and done, \Nwhat was this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that he's a cyborg, \Nhe must've originally been a person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who looked just like Bartholomew Kuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most natural possibility \Nis that he was a twin brother
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or a super look-alike who was modified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely no way to \Ncreate a live person from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PX-4...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rest a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect it to turn into \Nsuch an all-out fight so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to rest,\N but we really should hide first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get spotted again now, \Nwe'll all be caught in one fell swoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... wait just a tiny bit longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Another enemy?! \NWhere's that voice coming from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above! Above!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! You're a real disgrace, PX-4!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It costs as much as an entire warship \Nto build one Pacifista like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, now what am I supposed to \Ntell that lousy punk in my report?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:14.15,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}"Captain of Navy Headquarters Science Unit"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:16.80,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500)}"Sentomaru"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warlord of the Sea is still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real or not, we don't got enough \Nstrength left to fight that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say "Pacifista"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pacifista? That's like a pacifist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the name of the guy we just beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you, Battle Axe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you call people \Nby their weapons' names...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use asking me questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna tell you anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got the toughest defense in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.98,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, my mouth is sealed just as tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can at least tell us your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no reason to answer anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sentomaru, the most \Ntight-lipped guy in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. So you're Sentomaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I \Nvoluntarily told you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.42,0:18:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't answering your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin, PX-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shoots beams from his palms too! Not paws!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna think about it, \Nbut that means this is a third one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our safety is more important \Nthan that mystery right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One more fight,\N and we will be critically injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...before we even run into the admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.53,0:19:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not all together! \NWe'll split up in groups!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running sounds good to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us should split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! You gonna be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you, Nami-swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it costs me my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks! Now let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mellorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're ready to give up your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you can act as a decoy for all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Offer's for ladies only, you damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can protect your own \Ndamn self, Panty-Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-kun! Do everything you can \Nto protect me, okay?! Please?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Usopp! I'm hurt enough as it is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear not! I shall cover you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would imagine you're still quite damaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was witness to the entire \Nincident on Thriller Bark
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you stepped in for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's run there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so scared of beams now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Meet on the Sunny in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're splitting up! After them, PX-1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let 'em leave Grove #12! \NThings'll get ugly if they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Super Smoke Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! The bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Why's he coming after us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, hey, you! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went that way! You guys alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be \Nworried about other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that pirates mean anything to me, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attack power is quite nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have the greatest defense in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashigara Dokkoi Shove!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.48,0:21:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! This guy is strong, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I don't have powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something weird about his moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a friend, you brute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away! Get away from Zoro, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Z-Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-san's been hit by a beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, took you long enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About time you got here, Uncle Kizaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! That man is a navy admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.84,0:22:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.67,0:22:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late for you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.30,0:22:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 120 million bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.37,0:22:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that you're quite the swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.65,0:22:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a one-hit knockout?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.83,0:22:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your exhaustion must have really built up...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The admiral...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.36,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can have a nice, long rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.30,0:23:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a Warlord of the Sea, \Na weirdo with a battle axe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.87,0:23:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now a navy admiral?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let you guys escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll end up losing face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As we are now, we can't beat these guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone focus on escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.26,0:23:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.58,0:23:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Admiral Kizaru's Fierce Assault \NThe Straw Hats Face Certain Death!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
